title: Age of Empires II HD The African Kingdoms [MAC OS X][Wineskin]
description:
Age of Empires II HD: The African Kingdoms (c) SkyBox Labs 
Release Date : 11/2015

Install Instructions:
-Run DMG file
-Copy the Age of Empires II HD application to your Application Folder
-Play
-Keep Seeding & Leave Feedback (much appreciated)

Notes: this release is standalone and includes all released campaigns
so far:

- Age of Kings Campaign
- The Conquerers Campaign
- The Forgotten Campaign
- The African Kingdoms Campaign


General Notes:
Block any connections with Little Snitch, Although it also works fine without it..
So, not really necessary!

Wrapper Version : Wineskin 2.6.2
Engine : WS9Wine1.7.52
D3Dboost enabled
MacDriver instead of X11
Resolution set to Auto
